h3. Problem Definition

In this documentation; [JIRA 7.1.9 REST API {{api/2/}}|https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/server/#api/2/], the URL is invalid due to double "/":
 * [Get permissions|https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/server/#api/2/-getPermissions]: {{GET /rest/api/2//mypermissions}}
 * [Get all permissions|https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/server/#api/2/-getAllPermissions]: {{GET /rest/api/2//permissions}}

h3. Suggested Solution

The URL suppose to be:
 * [Get permissions|https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/server/#api/2/-getPermissions]: {{GET /rest/api/2/mypermissions}}
 * [Get all permissions|https://docs.atlassian.com/jira/REST/server/#api/2/-getAllPermissions]: {{GET /rest/api/2/permissions}}

